#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_causal_identification.ipynb:270002
#: c217d897566f49e0a5a607f638189dd2
msgid ""
"If we have PyMC installed, the simplest approach would be to include all our"
" variables in a model and run it. This is like using any model available on "
