msgid ""
"Great news! 🎉 Our model is nailing it when it comes to figuring out the "
"actual impact of our treatment variables. We managed to take into account "
"both the unseen confounders and the things we can see, like holidays."
msgstr ""
"¡Grandes noticias! 🎉 Nuestro modelo está logrando un excelente desempeño al "
"determinar el impacto real de nuestras variables de tratamiento. Hemos "
"conseguido tener en cuenta tanto los factores de confusión no visibles como "
"las cosas que podemos ver, como los días festivos."

#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_causal_identification.ipynb:670004
#: f541cb57f63044269bdbc555a9840c66
msgid ""
"You might have noticed we have variables like market growth that aren’t in "
